# The same local-only directory categories are forbidden at any nesting depth.
# Git paths always use `/`; bracket classes keep this effective on case-sensitive runners.
**/.[Cc][Ll][Aa][Uu][Dd][Ee]/**
**/.[Cc][Oo][Dd][Ee][Xx]/**
**/.[Cc][Oo][Dd][Ee][Xx]-[Ss][Kk][Ii][Nn]-[Ll][Oo][Cc][Aa][Ll]/**
**/.[Hh][Ii][Ss][Tt][Oo][Rr][Yy]/**
**/.[Ii][Dd][Ee][Aa]/**
**/.[Vv][Ss][Cc][Oo][Dd][Ee]/**
